Package arraylist_pkg

Class Comment

java.lang.Object
arraylist_pkg.Interaction
arraylist_pkg.Comment
public class Comment extends Interaction
The Comment class extends Interaction and represents a comment made by an Account on a Post. It contains the content of the comment and the Account who made the comment.
